About us
Any company that wants to offer payment and banking services faces numerous regulatory and technological barriers. Through Hash, any B2B company can offer its customers business advantages by eliminating transaction friction and offering other benefits related to their core operation. Our whitelabel and plug-and-play platform eliminates implementation time, reduces initial investment and operating costs by up to 95%.
We understand the value of collaboration, and we strive for a healthy work environment. Flexible work hours, pet friendly office, yoga, massage, etc. are cool, but they are simply a reflex of autonomy as a core value of our team

About the role
Our business is extremely abstract, and its nature has a high level of complexity. That's why we seek designers who can abstract, understand, and develop solutions at all levels of the organization. We believe that the essence of the area is to solve problems and materialize the intangible with purpose. Our team requires a high level of technical execution, zeal for their deliverables, and above all, deconstruct beliefs. Always seeking a diversity of perspectives, our designers cannot have attachment and ego about their deliverables.

To build this infrastructure, we need to design an amazing and scalable product. "Go horse culture" doesn't really work for the type of systems that we build. We tend to reduce technical debt and prioritize quality over a fast release.
We are not attached to a specific set of tools or frameworks, we have several challenges, and we are free to choose the best way to attack each one of them. Everyone in our team has the autonomy to develop the assigned projects directly with other roles.

What we are looking for
We are looking for people passionate about design. We need people who want to know more about our market, how the payment ecosystem works and help us to change it. We want people that connect with our business, and we want to build something that will change Brazil.

